        <h2>Opening Keynote Panel</h2> 
        <h3 class="program-titles">Reflection on “Dharma & Puṇya: Buddhist ritual art” and the later history of Nepal  
Jinah Kim & Todd Lewis</h3>
        <h5>5:30 – 6:30pm</h5>
        <h6>Lecture Hall, Lower Level<br>485 Broadway, Cambridge</h6>
        <h4>Reception <span class="date-style">6:30 – 7:30pm</span></h4>
        <h6>HAA living room, 4th floor<br>485 Broadway, Cambridge</h6>
        
        
         <hr class="schedule-rule">   


